Package: caspoc
Type: Package
Title: Double-split cross-validation with mixOmics spls
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael Widdowson, Jonathan Thorsen
Maintainer: Michael Widdowson <michael.widdowson@dbac.dk>, Jonathan Thorsen <jonathan.thorsen@dbac.dk>
Description: This package wraps the sparse Partial Least squares (spls) function from the excellent mixOmics package within a double-split cross-validation approach.
    It allows tuning of hyperparameters (keepX, keepY, ncomp) in one hold-out set, and leaves another hold-out set unbiased which can be used for inference.
